Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.10,Captions,,0,0,0,,It didn't work because\NKentucky is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:09.20,Captions,,0,0,0,,Kentucky is different from California\Nand New York. The patients are different...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:13.50,Captions,,0,0,0,,...from Brazil and London. The model was built\Non 400 million patients across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:17.40,Captions,,0,0,0,,What we needed was a model built\Non Kentucky patients...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:21.14,Captions,,0,0,0,,...with Kentucky data,\Nwith Kentucky problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:25.50,Captions,,0,0,0,,The Cabinet for Health and Family Services\Nhas a state-university partnership...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:30.00,Captions,,0,0,0,,...where you can propose getting access\Nto state data - super valuable data.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:33.46,Captions,,0,0,0,,Now it's up to us to figure out how to use\Nthat data to make healthcare better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.50,Captions,,0,0,0,,The final one is essentially\Ncancer screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:40.50,Captions,,0,0,0,,Can we get ahold of Medicaid claims data\Nand identify patients eligible for screening...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:44.80,Captions,,0,0,0,,...whether it's colon cancer, lung cancer,\Nor cervical cancer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:49.62,Captions,,0,0,0,,...find those patients, and deploy\Nsimilar software to reach out to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:53.00,Captions,,0,0,0,,We think we can design an AI agent\Nthat walks you through the process...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.60,Captions,,0,0,0,,...and schedules your appointment\Nat the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:00.40,Captions,,0,0,0,,...so you don't have to take the onus\Non yourself of calling your doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.60,Captions,,0,0,0,,...and trying to get a colonoscopy.\NWe can do it automatically...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.04,Captions,,0,0,0,,...bring you in, and make sure we are caring\Nfor the people of Kentucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:09.30,Captions,,0,0,0,,We don't want California.\NWe don't want New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:12.50,Captions,,0,0,0,,We want Kentucky's data\Nso we can better impact Kentuckians.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:15.70,Captions,,0,0,0,,We want this to be\Na dynamic conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:18.60,Captions,,0,0,0,,...about what we can do to streamline\Nand provide better access to data...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.30,Captions,,0,0,0,,...more quickly. Whatever we need to do\Non our side...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.84,Captions,,0,0,0,,...we want to be a good partner.
